Package sailpoint.object

Class RoleAssignment

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      • sailpoint.object.Assignment
        • sailpoint.object.RoleAssignment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RoleRequest
    public class RoleAssignment
extends Assignment
    Used to record information about role assignments and revocations. This is similar to AttributeMetadata but different in that changes are being recorded to individual values of a single multi-valued attribute. A list of these will be stored in the preferences area of the identity cube. This was re-actored in 6.0 and now extends Assignment
    See Also:
    Assignment, AttributeAssignment, Serialized Form
